ing out of last year's Australian Open at the 11th hour and has played only one tour match since the Japan Open in October 2022.\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1491, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kyrgios\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1303}, {\"ngram\": \"knee\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1327}, {\"ngram\": \"foot\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1333}, {\"ngram\": \"wrist injuries\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1352}, {\"ngram\": \"last year's Australian Open\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"the 11th hour\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1418}, {\"ngram\": \"only one tour match\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1453}, {\"ngram\": \"the Japan Open\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1474}, {\"ngram\": \"October\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In his absence from court, Kyrgios has started building a media career and on Tuesday made his debut as an on-court interviewer at the Australian Open, chatting with his friend Novak Djokovic after the world number one's quarter-final.\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1670, \"end\": 1684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his absence\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1507}, {\"ngram\": \"court\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1518}, {\"ngram\": \"Kyrgios\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"a media career\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1578}, {\"ngram\": \"his debut\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1593}, {\"ngram\": \"court\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1608}, {\"ngram\": \"the Australian Open\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1643}, {\"ngram\": \"his friend\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1669}, {\"ngram\": \"the world number\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1707}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kyrgios said last month that he would play on for two more seasons at best and on Wednesday wrote he was looking forward to continuing the media work after retirement.\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1897, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kyrgios\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1737}, {\"ngram\": \"two more seasons\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1796}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1821}, {\"ngram\": \"the media work\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 1879}, {\"ngram\": \"retirement\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The winner of seven ATP Tour titles, Kyrgios has had a chequered relationship with his fellow Australians.\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 2005, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The winner\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1909}, {\"ngram\": \"seven ATP Tour titles\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1934}, {\"ngram\": \"Kyrgios\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 1943}, {\"ngram\": \"a chequered relationship\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1976}, {\"ngram\": \"his fellow Australians\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 2004}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His on-court histrionics and frequent disciplinary issues alienated many fans and was the reason behind Chiller's caution in 2016 as she looked to clean up team culture after a scandal involving the swimming team at the 2012 Olympics in London.\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2111, \"end\": 2118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chiller\", \"score\": 0.9578597795740752, \"rank\": 0.043994143322449886, \"text\": \"Chiller\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chiller\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chiller\"}, {\"begin\": 2244, \"end\": 2250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999975890772889, \"rank\": 1.5636358732414346e-06, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L